Package bto.Model

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • bto.Model.User
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Applicant, Manager, Officer
    public abstract class User
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a user in the system. This is an abstract class that serves as the base for specific user types such as Applicant, Manager, and Officer.
